    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Note 2: The column titled ‘comments on proposed policy’ relates to the policy explained in the Consultation Paper (“CP”). The column titled ‘comments on proposed legislation’ refers to the draft legislation reflecting the proposed policy. ",
        "bbox": [
            58,
            305,
            932,
            347
